{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_0167aJT4r6XAz3mJkRhmCDet","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three replica set members are healthy (1 PRIMARY, 2 SECONDARY). The certificate rotation is complete.\n\n**Summary of what was done:**\n\n1. **Extracted** the CA cert and key from the `mongodb-tls-ca` secret\n2. **Generated** a new RSA-2048 server key in the `openssl-toolbox` pod\n3. **Created** a CSR with all required SANs preserved (localhost, mongo, mongo.mongodb, mongo.mongodb.svc, mongo.mongodb.svc.cluster.local, and all three pod DNS names)\n4. **Signed** the cert with the existing CA — valid from 2026-06-25 to **2027-06-25** (~1 year), issued by the unchanged `CN=mongo-ca`\n5. **Updated** the `mongodb-tls-cert` secret with the new `server.pem` (cert + key)\n6. **Rolling-restarted** the StatefulSet — Kubernetes replaced one pod at a time, keeping 2/3 members up throughout, so the replica set never lost quorum\n\nThe MongoDB cluster is now serving the new certificate and all three members are online."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":309,"cache_read_input_tokens":43773,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":309},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0bb4f7bf-7fad-4c8f-a19e-54e7ea04441e","uuid":"56597f9f-0bcc-41c7-927b-9e7d0f477ac5","request_id":"req_011CcPqLqrXDg7xrQsfDMKCA"}
